---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import surroundingsImg1 from "../assets/images/surroundings/5x7/göholm_surroundings_01.webp";
import cookingImg1 from "../assets/images/surroundings/5x7/göholm_cooking_01.webp";
import cookingImg2 from "../assets/images/surroundings/5x7/göholm_cooking_02.webp";
import cookingImg3 from "../assets/images/surroundings/5x7/göholm_cooking_03.webp";
import cookingImg4 from "../assets/images/surroundings/7x5/göholm_cooking_04.webp";
import landscapeImg2 from "../assets/images/surroundings/4x5/göholm_landscape_02.webp";
import landscapeImg4 from "../assets/images/surroundings/5x7/göholm_landscape_04.webp";
import landscapeImg5 from "../assets/images/surroundings/4x5/göholm_landscape_05.webp";
import landscapeImg6 from "../assets/images/surroundings/5x7/göholm_landscape_06.webp";
import fishingImg1 from "../assets/images/surroundings/4x5/göholm_fishing_01.webp";
import fishingImg2 from "../assets/images/surroundings/4x5/göholm_fishing_02.webp";
import fishingImg3 from "../assets/images/surroundings/5x7/göholm_fishing_03.webp";
import fishingImg4 from "../assets/images/surroundings/7x5/göholm_fishing_04.webp";
---

<MainLayout title="Surroundings">
  <section class="py-80">
    <div class="max-w-[960px] mx-auto">

      <!-- ========================= INTRO (Skall-style) ========================= -->
    <section class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-32 md:grid-cols-12 md:gap-x-32 items-end">
  
  <!-- LEFT: Title block (bundjusteret) -->
  <div class="md:col-span-4 self-end">
    <h1 class="mb-16">Surroundings</h1>
    <h3>the nature at Göholm</h3>
  </div>

  <!-- RIGHT: Hero image -->
  <div class="md:col-span-7 md:col-start-6">
    <div class="aspect-[5/7]">
      <img
        src={surroundingsImg1.src}
        alt="Göholm surroundings"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>
    </div>

    </section>


<!-- INTRO TEXT: TWO COLUMNS -->
<div class="mt-80 grid grid-cols-1 gap-32 md:grid-cols-2">
  <p>
    Göholm is surrounded by open fields where cattle graze slowly through
    the seasons — a living part of the estate’s agricultural heritage.
    The manor lies just ten kilometres south of Ronneby, set within a
    landscape that stretches across 733 hectares.
  </p>

  <p>
    These pastures and forests shape the rhythm of everyday life at Göholm
    — peaceful, grounded and guided by nature. The grazing cattle, the
    shifting light over the fields and the vastness.
  </p>
</div>



      <!-- ========================= CONTENT (same rules as Chambers) ========================= -->
      <div class="mt-112 flex flex-col gap-112">

        <!-- OUTDOOR COOKING: IMAGE LEFT + TEXT RIGHT (TEXT BOTTOM-ALIGNED) -->
        <article class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-32 md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-x-32 items-stretch">
          <div class="aspect-[4/5]">
            <img
              src={cookingImg1.src}
              alt="Outdoor Cooking Göholm"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col justify-end w-full max-w-[420px]">
            <h2 class="mb-16">Outdoor Cooking</h2>

            <p class="mb-16">
              With a short UTV ride, you reach one of Göholm’s most beautiful
              viewpoints – an open plateau overlooking the sea, the forest and the
              surrounding rock formations. Here, a simple and functional fire pit
              allows guests to cook meals over open flames.
            </p>

            <p class="mb-16">
              On warm days, the area feels bright and expansive, while in winter it
              offers snow, frost and clear horizons, with the fire providing a
              natural gathering point.
            </p>

            <p>
              It’s a place to meet, share a meal, enjoy the view and become part of
              the landscape – with nothing but nature and the glow of the fire as
              the setting.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- TWO IMAGES SIDE BY SIDE (hairline gap) + CAPTION UNDER RIGHT -->
        <article class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-32 md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-x-1 items-start">
          <div class="aspect-[5/7]">
            <img
              src={cookingImg2.src}
              alt="Outdoor Cooking Göholm - UTV"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>

          <div>
  <div class="aspect-[5/7]">
    <img
      src={cookingImg3.src}
      alt="Outdoor Cooking Göholm - bonfire"
      class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      loading="lazy"
    />
  </div>

  <p class="caption mt-2 w-full max-w-[420px]">
    In the October season, it offers a modest way to be outdoors, close
    to nature, with the fire at the centre of it all.
  </p>
</div>

        </article>

   <!-- CENTERED COOKING + CAPTION -->
<article class="max-w-[640px] mx-auto mb-32">
  <div class="aspect-[7/5]">
    <img
      src={cookingImg4.src}
      alt="Outdoor Cooking Göholm - winter spot"
      class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      loading="lazy"
    />
  </div>

  <p class="caption mt-8 w-full max-w-[420px]">
    A quiet winter spot where the landscape opens toward the sea and the air
    feels crisp and clear.
  </p>
</article>

<!-- LARGE LANDSCAPE VIDEO -->
<section class="w-full mb-32">
  <div class="aspect-[16/9]">
    <video
      src="/videos/goholm_landscape_01.mp4"
      class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      autoplay
      muted
      loop
      playsinline
    ></video>
  </div>
</section>


        <!-- IMAGE LEFT + VIDEO RIGHT -->
        <article class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-32 md:grid-cols-12 md:gap-x-32 items-start">
          <div class="md:col-span-4 md:mt-32 w-full max-w-[420px]">
            <div class="aspect-[4/5]">
              <img
                src={landscapeImg2.src}
                alt="Cow landscape at Göholm"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </div>

            <p class="caption mt-2 w-full max-w-[420px]">
              The beautiful fields surrounding the estate.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="aspect-[4/5] overflow-hidden md:col-span-7 md:col-start-6">
            <video
              autoplay
              muted
              loop
              playsinline
              preload="metadata"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            >
              <source src="/videos/goholm_landscape_03.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
            </video>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- LANDSCAPE: IMAGE LEFT + TEXT RIGHT -->
        <article class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-32 md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-x-32 items-stretch">
          <div class="aspect-[4/5]">
            <img
              src={landscapeImg4.src}
              alt="Landscape at Göholm"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col justify-center w-full max-w-[420px]">
            <h2 class="mb-16">Landscape</h2>

            <p class="mb-16">
              Göholm’s landscape invites exploration, from soft forest paths beneath
              birch and oak to open clearings where the light moves gently across
              the ground. Walk, hike or simply wander at your own pace, moving
              through woodland, open pastures and toward the nearby coastline.
            </p>

            <p>
              The area offers shifting views, grazing animals and quiet places to
              pause along the way, creating a calm and natural sense of connection
              to the surroundings.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- IMAGE LEFT + IMAGE RIGHT -->
        <article class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-32 md:grid-cols-12 md:gap-x-32 items-start">
          <div class="md:col-span-4 md:mt-32 w-full max-w-[420px]">
            <div class="aspect-[4/5]">
              <img
                src={landscapeImg5.src}
                alt="Sheep in front of house"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="aspect-[5/7] md:col-span-7 md:col-start-6">
            <img
              src={landscapeImg6.src}
              alt="Red house Göholm surroundings"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- FISHING: TWO IMAGES SIDE BY SIDE + CAPTION UNDER RIGHT (hairline gap) -->
        <article class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-32 md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-x-1 items-start">
          <div class="w-full max-w-[420px]">
            <div class="aspect-[4/5]">
              <img
                src={fishingImg1.src}
                alt="View over the lake"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="w-full max-w-[420px]">
            <div class="aspect-[4/5]">
              <img
                src={fishingImg2.src}
                alt="On the way to go fishing"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </div>

            <p class="caption mt-2 w-full max-w-[420px]">
              The property’s lake for summer swims and peaceful fishing.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- FISHING: IMAGE LEFT + TEXT RIGHT -->
        <article class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-32 md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-x-32 items-stretch">
          <div class="aspect-[4/5]">
            <img
              src={fishingImg3.src}
              alt="Fishing at Göholm"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col justify-center w-full max-w-[420px]">
            <h2 class="mb-16">Fishing</h2>

            <p class="mb-16">
              Göholm is surrounded by oak forests, open landscapes and walking trails that lead into the Gö nature reserve.
              Here, fishing becomes a quiet ritual — early mornings with stillness over the water or soft evening light settling across the horizon.
            </p>

            <p>
              Regardless of experience, guests can enjoy the simple calm of casting a line in peaceful, untouched surroundings.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- CENTERED FISHING SPOT -->
        <article class="max-w-[640px] mx-auto">
          <div class="aspect-[7/5]">
            <img
              src={fishingImg4.src}
              alt="Fishing at Göholm - winter"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- LIST -->
        <article class="space-y-32">
          <div>
            <h2 class="mb-16">APR – OCT &nbsp;&nbsp; FISHING</h2>
            <div class="border-t border-manor-red-500"></div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="mb-16">SEP – FEB &nbsp;&nbsp; HUNTING SEASON</h2>
            <div class="border-t border-manor-red-500"></div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="mb-8">MAY – OCT &nbsp;&nbsp; GOLF</h2>
            <p class="mb-16">(courses open, best conditions June–Sep)</p>
            <div class="border-t border-manor-red-500"></div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="mb-16">APR – NOV &nbsp;&nbsp; UTV / ATV RIDING</h2>
            <div class="border-t border-manor-red-500"></div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="mb-8">YEAR – ROUND &nbsp;&nbsp;OUTDOOR ADVENTURES</h2>
            <p class="mb-16">(Hiking, exploring forests, coastline activities)</p>
            <div class="border-t border-manor-red-500"></div>
          </div>
        </article>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
